
<header class="box-header column col-12">
  <div class="box-title h5">Website Content</div>
  <p>Ah yes, the actual magic! The place where you give me the info I need to turn your businesses story into online marketing. This section will take some time to complete - try not to rush it! Everything you tell me about your business here, will be turned into content on your website. If you're struggling, don't hesitate to give me a shout and I'll walk you though it. </p>

</header>
<section class="box-body column col-12">
  <div class="columns no-margin-offset">       
    <%= render 'form', about_content: @about_content %>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="divider" ></div>
<footer class="box-footer column col-12 is-flex-centered">
  <% unless current_user.is_submitted? %>
    <%= link_to 'Preview Integrations Data', about_content_path(@about_content), class: 'btn', method: :get, confirm: "If you have unsaved changes, they'll vanish ðŸ˜¤. Make sure you've hit save first!" %> 
  <% else %>
    <button class="btn" disabled="" tabindex="-1">Edit Website Content</button> 
    <p>
       Your Site has already been submitted. If you see a problem with your submitted data, <%= link_to 'get in touch', pages_contact_path %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
</footer>
